standard_anchor(im_grade3_u4_l8, ccss, "3.OA.C.7", "Fluently multiply and divide within 100, using strategies such as the relationship between multiplication and division (e.g., knowing that $8 \\times 5 = 40$, one knows $40 \\div 5 = 8$) or properties of operations. By the end of Grade 3, know from memory all products of two one-digit numbers.").
